/* eslint-disable jsx-a11y/iframe-has-title */ /* eslint-disable no-unused-vars */ // Contactus.js import React, { useState } from "react"; import emailjs from "emailjs-com"; import { useTranslation } from "react-i18next"; function Contactus() { const { t } = useTranslation(); const [expanded, setExpanded] = useState(false); const toggleNav = () => { setExpanded(!expanded); }; const handleClick = () => { window.scrollTo(0, 0); setExpanded(false); }; function sendEmail(e) { e.preventDefault(); emailjs .sendForm( "service_lp35s39", "template_giqb4o4", e.target, "7LseggvnGoIcgGHia" ) .then( (result) => { console.log(result.text); alert(t("Email başarıyla gönderildi!")); }, (error) => { console.log(error.text); alert(t("Email gönderilirken bir hata oluştu!")); } ); e.target.reset(); } return ( <>
{t("BİZİMLE İLETİŞİME GEÇİN")}

0546 534 1963

Nilüfer / BURSA
